{"tid":2107799,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"輕度智障男涉藏清潔劑判囚准保釋上訴 警另控參與非法集結今提堂","createTime":"2020-07-14T06:18:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T07:16:00.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"348aff2caa59c04f7b486adfd72ae508696761ab","tid":2107799,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T06:18:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200714/AYBDKU2CBLFFCX3773KLU3ROKE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200714%2FAYBDKU2CBLFFCX3773KLU3ROKE%2F&d=nqzd6QM3TLyrPp4uhCfCn0t47LdDf8L2Tg6pYSR3Psk%3D&h=085c30bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200714%2FAYBDKU2CBLFFCX3773KLU3ROKE%2F&h=c6f2a96b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200714/AYBDKU2CBLFFCX3773KLU3ROKE/</a><br />\n<br />\n智商只如11歲小童的輕度弱智清潔工「發仔」，今年1月涉於屯門藏有清潔劑、石油氣及雷射筆，早前承認在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器；署理主任裁判官張潔宜指輕度智障並非減刑理由，判監8個月，但准他保釋等候上訴。惟清潔工被指另涉於去年10月在旺角警署外參與非法集結、蒙面及管有雷射筆，再度遭起訴，今早與同案另外兩名被告在西九龍裁判法院應訊。裁判官應辯方要求，將聆訊押後至9月22日再處理，其間被告須遵守控方提出的嚴格擔保條件、包括宵禁及禁足令。"},{"pid":"f1fda08eef233a53e3c414cc73a031f5bfb4162e","tid":2107799,"uid":124277,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T06:23:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6e7f0317faa1f54644830ee77ed45100cb85a839","tid":2107799,"uid":202425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1fda08eef233a53e3c414cc73a031f5bfb4162e","tid":2107799,"uid":124277,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T06:23:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T06:30:23.000Z","msg":"你把口都幾衰"},{"pid":"c1b4c254b5c9360bc9b6d7f3420e2554b5a9678e","tid":2107799,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6e7f0317faa1f54644830ee77ed45100cb85a839","tid":2107799,"uid":202425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1fda08eef233a53e3c414cc73a031f5bfb4162e","tid":2107799,"uid":124277,"like":0,"dislike":9,"sco